      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Black dress</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>I came here to see you, </l>
          <l>We have to talk about </l>
          <l>the things that made me hate you </l>
          <l>the things that on your mind. </l>
          <l>you know i used to love you </l>
          <l>back then you were so pretty </l>
          <l>wearing the black dress ,Saturday morning </l>
          <l>we were always on our way. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>...and then when something happened </l>
          <l>you knew that i'll be fine </l>
          <l>although you drive me crazy </l>
          <l>you always make me smile, </l>
          <l>you know i used to love you </l>
          <l>waited long long time </l>
          <l>for you to say you love me, </l>
          <l>for you to say "you're mine"</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
